1st create & execute Dockerfile by:
>> docker build .

2nd create & execute docker-compose.yml by:
>> docker-compose build

3rd create django project by docker-compose and sh -c by:
>> docker-compose run app sh -c "django-admin.py startproject app ."

4th syn our git push origin to travis-ci & create .travis.yml

5th create flake8 config to django project .flake8

